                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;>With 48 countries and nearly 2,300 languages, Asia is defined by a wide spectrum of customs, religious beliefs and cultures. The Asian Leadership Network fosters belonging and inclusion and fosters a workplace where every voice is heard and valued.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>The Asian Leadership Network fosters a diverse and inclusive environment where every voice is heard and valued. ALN promotes a sense of belonging and community by enabling all employees to reach their full potential. We do this through:&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Raising awareness about cultural diversity&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Informal mentoring and networking&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Business and patient impact&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
